Package com.redis.app.redis_app_studio.shared

Class SCLogger

java.lang.Object
com.redis.app.redis_app_studio.shared.SCLogger
public class SCLogger extends Object
The SmartClient logger class leverages the SmartClient logger stream for generating log messages related to data items, docs, grids and DSCriteria.
